The,Oracle,Service,Cloud,Knowledge,Advanced,API,provides,numerous,functionalities,for,accessing,and,developing,knowledge,resources,The,API,facilitates,the,addition,modification,and,interaction,with,cloud,based,knowledge,resources,It,allows,users,to,search,and,make,recommendations,for,articles,in,addition,to,accessing,user,information,from,external,apps,This,API,allows,developers,to,customize,Oracle,Service,Cloud,applications,and,integrate,third,party,applications,Developers,can,also,use,it,to,integrate,Oracle,s,suites,of,applications,including,Siebel,and,E,Business,Suite,The,API,sends,HTTP,formatted,requests,and,returns,JSON,formatted,responses